    public abstract class UiWidgetCustomListTable<ROW>
extends UiWidgetCustomAbstractListTable<ROW,UiWidgetListTable<ROW>>
implements UiWidgetListTable<ROW>
    This is the abstract base class for a custom widget implementing UiWidgetListTable. A subclass should set the columns and other options to configure a ready-to-use list that can be easily reused.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
